rows.label: qst200421_msg0001
rows.name:
You all did great, mo! Thank
you for protecting me, mo!

rows.label: qst200421_msg0002
rows.name:
I will definitely repay
this favor someday, mo!

rows.label: qst200421_msg0003
rows.name:
...I merely did what was natural.
There is no need for thanks.

rows.label: qst200421_msg0005
rows.name:
Sheesh, Vasara just won't listen when
I say teamwork is important, mo.

rows.label: qst200421_msg0006
rows.name:
Tora and friends will follow
Vasara, mo! Punin-san will
also work hard, mo!

rows.label: qst200421_msg0008
rows.name: That was a lot of trouble, wasn't it?

rows.label: qst200421_msg0009
rows.name:
But you got your revenge. I'm
sure Ellenora-san is happy too.

rows.label: qst200421_msg0010
rows.name: That was tough, but we managed.

rows.label: qst200421_msg0011
rows.name:
And we got our revenge. I'm sure
Ellenora-san would be pleased.

rows.label: qst200421_msg0012
rows.name:
It took some time, but
we got our revenge.

rows.label: qst200421_msg0013
rows.name:
Ellenora-san might be happy
now, wherever she is.

rows.label: qst200421_msg0014
rows.name:
Good work. It was a bit of a
struggle this time, but...

rows.label: qst200421_msg0015
rows.name:
We got our revenge. I bet
Ellenora-san is happy too.

rows.label: qst200421_msg0017
rows.name:
As long as there are those who
must be judged, I will continue
to judge them with this sword.

rows.label: qst200421_msg0018
rows.name: That is all there is to it.
